# 多模块程序的日志输出到不同文件


## 更新日志
2021-04-19 V1.0.2 解决使用TimedRotatingFileHandler做日志分割，Python多进程启动时，出现下面错误的问题
```
PermissionError: [WinError 32] 另一个程序正在使用此文件，进程无法访问。: xxxx -> xxxx
```


## 安装

```
pip install epic-logger -i https://pypi.org/simple/
```

## 使用

package1.py

```
from EpicLogger.logger import InfoLogger, DebugLogger, ErrorLogger, WarningLogger, CriticalLogger

info_logger = InfoLogger(__name__, "E:/logs/test01.log")
debug_logger = DebugLogger(__name__, "E:/logs/test01.log")
error_logger = ErrorLogger(__name__, "E:/logs/test01.log")
warning_logger = WarningLogger(__name__, "E:/logs/test02.log")
critical_logger = CriticalLogger(__name__, "E:/logs/test02.log")


def say_hi():
    info_logger.log('Hi! Message 1 Log Into E:/logs/test01.log')
    debug_logger.log('Hi! Message 2 Log Into E:/logs/test01.log')
    debug_logger.log('Hi! Message 3 Log Into E:/logs/test01.log')
    error_logger.log('Hi! Message 4 Log Into E:/logs/test01.log')
    error_logger.log('Hi! Message 5 Log Into E:/logs/test01.log')
    warning_logger.log('Hi! Message 6 Log Into E:/logs/test02.log')
    critical_logger.log('Hi! Message 7 Log Into E:/logs/test02.log')


if __name__ == "__main__":
    say_hi()

```

